title: Lowertown Living with great location
posting_body: ['200 East 10th Street, Saint Paul, MN 55101', 'Renaissance Box offers efficiency, one-, and two-bedroom apartment homes in a historic renovation.', 'Loft-style apartments boast floor-to-ceiling windows, stunning views and stunning original features.', 'These affordable apartment homes are for individuals earning low to moderate incomes.', 'Income restrictions apply.', 'Amenities Include:', 'On-site Laundry', 'Abundant natural lighting', 'Central heating & cooling', 'Located in a rapidly-growing, mixed-use residential community centered around Wacouta Commons Park', 'Smoke-Free Community', 'Elevator', 'Exposed brick interior', 'Near Light Rail-', 'Green Line', 'Fitness Center', 'Electronic Thermostat', 'Easy access to Interstates 94E and 35E, and Highways 10 and 52', 'Community room with full kitchen and restrooms', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'email:renaissancebox at aeon dot org', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised apartment.', 'Please contact us today for the most updated information.', 'Professionally managed by Aeon, a provider of Fair housing and Equal Opportunity']
